Nginx Web Server Install

This explanation was made in the centos 7 operating system.

1. yum -y update

2. sudo yum install epel-release -y

3. sudo yum install nginx -y

4. sudo systemctl enable nginx

5. sudo systemctl start nginx

6. sudo systemctl status nginx

7. Editting Nginx Conf

/etc/nginx/conf.d/default.conf

8. Nginx Config

/etc/nginx/nginx.conf

9. systemctl stop firewalld

10. systemctl disable firewalld